data.description: A remarkable property; nearly 32 acres of prime hunting land along with approximately 1.5 acre stocked pond. This tastefully updated, well-maintained 3 bedroom 1 bath home is a rare find in the Marshall area. New laminate floors flow through the open concept main floor- from living room, dining room, to kitchen w/ newer stainless steel appliances. Two bedrooms are on the main floor along with full bathroom & laundry. The third bedroom is on the upper level along with a landing space that makes a great home office, sitting area, etc. 2 large pole barns, both w/ concrete floor & electric; the largest barn is insulated and heated. There is also an open storage barn for equipment storage. Mowed trails provide access to the entire property. There is an insulated cabin (accessory building) w/ electric & large dock providing access to the approx. 1.5 acre stocked pond. Outdoor wood boiler provides heat to the house for efficient heat, along with a newer propane forced air furnace as a secondary heat source & central air conditioning. A peaceful rural setting, but conveniently located minutes from the City of Marshall, I94, and I69.
